Remote file monitoring system

A web application which logs changes done on a file which is situated at a remote server.

Must have:
1. File should be located remotely.
Changes in the file should be instantly reflected on the client page.
2. Client Page should load the last 15 lines from the file. It should be able to append or delete lines on a real time basis.

Good to have:
1.Different filters on the client page.
2.Prettified client page to consume data.